title: #111 - Brendan Schaub & ME
description: Mixed Martial Artist & co-hosts of The Fighter & the Kid podcast, Brendan Schaub & I hang in the Mancave & talk about Kimbo Slice, what it's like fighting in the UFC, Cadbury Eggs & his eating disorder, & Morning Beers & my drinking problem.
